    "description": "Nobody is a 2021 American action thriller film directed by Ilya Naishuller and written by Derek Kolstad. It stars Bob Odenkirk as a mild-mannered family man who returns to his former life of an assassin after his family and he become the target of a vengeful crime lord. Connie Nielsen, RZA, and Christopher Lloyd appear in supporting roles. Odenkirk and David Leitch are among the film's producers.",
